data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: The U.S. Marine Corps War Memorial is undergoing a restoration process. The Marine Corps War Memorial had two campaigns added to the memorial. For a descriptive transcript text document of this production, contact Kim Hardison at kimberly.hardison@usmc.mil.
